msgid "ANIME"
msgstr "アニメ"

#: .\templates\portfolio_app\hobbies.html:153
msgid ""
"\"Starting with classics like Pokémon and Dragon Ball, I have now completed "
"over 100 series. Anime was a key factor in helping me learn Japanese; I "
"transitioned from dubs and subs to watching in original Japanese, which "
"allowed me to truly understand the language and culture. From the grand "
"adventure of One Piece and Hunter x Hunter to the strategic depth of "
"Classroom of the Elite and Dr. Stone, anime has shaped my perspective on "
"storytelling and perseverance.\""
msgstr ""
"ポケモンやドラゴンボール等の名作に触れ、現在は100以上のシリーズを視聴しまし"
"た。アニメは日本語学習の大きな助けとなり、現在はオリジナル版で文化と言語を深"
"く理解できるようになりました。"

